00:10:16.850 --> 00:10:18.400
And they all have really
high scores.

00:10:18.400 --> 00:10:21.390
And you're like, I don't want to
destroy your guys's score,

00:10:21.390 --> 00:10:23.750
but really, we need to get that
off there so people can

00:10:23.750 --> 00:10:24.140
have a chance.

00:10:24.140 --> 00:10:26.590
TODD KERPELMAN: All right,
makes sense.

00:10:26.590 --> 00:10:29.750
Now, using this tool, could I--
for instance, my customer

00:10:29.750 --> 00:10:32.040
service people, someone emails
me and says, hey, I didn't get

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:32.750
