achievements for them.

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:43.430
TODD KERPELMAN: So the idea is
this is really used for--

00:10:43.430 --> 00:10:44.850
WOLFF DOBSON: For unrevealed--

00:10:44.850 --> 00:10:45.720
set back to revealed.

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:46.850
TODD KERPELMAN: So this
