again, only if you're an owner

00:11:00.260 --> 00:11:01.090
of the application.

00:11:01.090 --> 00:11:01.420
TODD KERPELMAN: Yeah.

00:11:01.420 --> 00:11:03.920
I guess that links into our
third question-- sort of what

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:05.240
you mentioned.

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:07.480
How do I know who has access
to these tools?

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:07.680
WOLFF DOBSON: Right.

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:11.450
So for the testing tools, you
just need to be on the tester

00:11:11.450 --> 00:11:14.600
