developer console.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:16.350
TODD KERPELMAN: And chances
are-- that's the one you've

00:11:16.350 --> 00:11:19.000
got to add so that people can
try your game before any game

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:20.250
services has been published,
basically.

00:11:20.250 --> 00:11:20.970
WOLFF DOBSON: Right.

00:11:20.970 --> 00:11:23.450
And the owner of the application
is the person who

00:11:23.450 --> 00:11:25.024
can do the hiding
and unhiding.

00:11:25.024 --> 00:11:25.910
TODD KERPELMAN: OK.

00:11:25.910 --> 00:11:27.450
WOLFF DOBSON: And you have to
sign in as that person when

00:11:27.450 --> 00:11:28.950
